```plantuml
@startuml freenowtech_AndroidCI

actor Developer
participant "Git Repository" as Git
participant "Jenkins Server" as Jenkins
participant "Docker Host" as Docker
participant "Android SDK Container" as AndroidContainer

Developer -> Git: Pushes code changes
Git -> Jenkins: Triggers build (webhook)
Jenkins -> Docker: Requests build environment
Docker -> AndroidContainer: Creates instance
AndroidContainer -> Jenkins: Reports ready status

group Build Process
    Jenkins -> AndroidContainer: Pulls latest code
    AndroidContainer -> Jenkins: Code received
    Jenkins -> AndroidContainer: Executes build commands
    AndroidContainer -> Jenkins: Build status
    alt Build Success
        Jenkins -> Docker: Releases container
        Jenkins -> Developer: Notifies success
    else Build Failure
        Jenkins -> Docker: Releases container
        Jenkins -> Developer: Notifies failure
    end
end

@enduml
```